  "body": "I wrote some tests depend on multiple transactions in one block. They work well in ganache with miner_stop and evm_mine methods. But they don't work when migrate to hardhat because no miner_stop method. Is there a way to insert multiple transactions into one block in hardhat? or any plan to support this?\r\n\r\nIt seems this [PR 1087](https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/pull/1087) is related to what I want. Any plan when to release it?",
